---
// ResultsSection.astro — Frontier VLM benchmark + our training results
---
<section id="results" class="content-section">
  <div class="section-container">
    <h2 class="section-title">Results</h2>

    <h3 class="results-h3">Frontier VLM benchmark on ViewSuite-5K test (530 view pairs)</h3>
