      Accuracy / Success&nbsp;Rate (%) on Short (<em>d</em>&nbsp;&lt;&nbsp;3) and Long (<em>d</em>&nbsp;≥&nbsp;3) splits.
      Best in each column is <strong>bold</strong>.
    </p>

