    <h3 class="results-h3 tres-h3">Results on Interactive View Planning</h3>
    <p class="results-lead">
      Success rate (%) under the calibrated 0.5&nbsp;m / 30° threshold. Our framework lifts a 7B model
      from <strong>2.5% → 47.8%</strong>, beating every proprietary VLM evaluated.
    </p>

    <div class="results-table-wrap small-table">
      <table class="results-table">
        <thead>
          <tr><th class="method-col">Method</th><th>Short</th><th>Long</th><th>All</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr class="row-header"><td colspan="4">Prompting Baselines</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Qwen2.5-VL-7B-Instruct</td><td>7.1</td><td>0.0</td><td>2.5</td></tr>
          <tr><td>GPT-5.4 Pro</td><td>32.6</td><td>11.0</td><td>18.5</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Gemini 3.1 Pro</td><td>28.8</td><td>17.4</td><td>21.4</td></tr>
          <tr class="row-header"><td colspan="4">Training Baselines</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Direct PPO</td><td>7.0</td><td>1.2</td><td>3.2</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Direct GRPO (filter)</td><td>10.8</td><td>2.2</td><td>5.2</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Success-Only Bootstrapping</td><td>14.0</td><td>2.0</td><td>6.2</td></tr>
          <tr class="row-header"><td colspan="4">Ablations of Our Framework</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Random-graph</td><td>25.4</td><td>6.4</td><td>13.0</td></tr>
          <tr><td>1 iter + RL</td><td>24.3</td><td>5.4</td><td>12.0</td></tr>
          <tr><td>2 iter + RL</td><td>49.7</td><td>16.2</td><td>27.9</td></tr>
          <tr class="row-header ours"><td colspan="4">Ours (Self-Exploration + View Graph Distillation, 3 iters)</td></tr>
          <tr class="ours-row"><td>Qwen2.5-VL-7B-Instruct</td><td><b>67.2</b></td><td><b>36.9</b></td><td><b>47.8</b></td></tr>
          <tr class="ours-row"><td>Qwen3-VL-8B-Instruct</td><td><b>56.8</b></td><td><b>19.4</b></td><td><b>32.5</b></td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .results-h3 {
    color: #1e1b4b;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    margin: 0 auto 0.4rem auto;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .tres-h3 { margin-top: 3rem; }
  .results-lead {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto 1.25rem auto;
    text-align: center;
    color: #2e2a55;
    font-size: 0.98rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }
  .results-lead em { font-style: italic; color: #5b21b6; }
  .results-lead strong { color: #4338ca; }

  .results-table-wrap {
    max-width: 1080px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    overflow-x: auto;
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid #e0e7ff;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 14px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.08);
    padding: 1rem;
  }
  .small-table { max-width: 720px; }

  .results-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    color: #2e2a55;
  }
  .results-table th, .results-table td {
    padding: 6px 10px;
    text-align: center;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .results-table thead th {
    background: #eef2ff;
    color: #312e81;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .results-table th.grp { border-bottom: 2px solid #c7d2fe; }
  .results-table .grp-p2v { color: #4338ca; }
  .results-table .grp-v2p { color: #6d28d9; }
  .results-table .grp-ivp { color: #be185d; }
  .results-table .model-col, .results-table .method-col {
    text-align: left;
    min-width: 170px;
  }
  .results-table tbody td:first-child { text-align: left; }
  .results-table .row-baseline td { background: #f5f6ff; font-style: italic; }
  .results-table .row-header td {
    background: #eef2ff;
    color: #4338ca;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-align: left;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }
  .results-table .row-header.ours td {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #6366f1, #4f46e5);
    color: #fff;
  }
  .results-table .ours-row td { background: #fdf4ff; font-weight: 600; color: #5b21b6; }
  .results-table .ours-row td:first-child { color: #4338ca; }
  .results-table tbody tr:hover td { background: #faf5ff; }
  .results-table .ours-row:hover td { background: #fae8ff; }
</style>
